# Naming Conventions

## General

- Use clear, readable names — avoid abbreviations and technical jargon
- Variables and functions: `camelCase` with descriptive intent
- Types and interfaces: `PascalCase`
- Config constants: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE` (e.g. `DEFAULT_PAGE_SIZE`, `MAX_UPLOAD_SIZE`)

## Files

| Folder | Pattern | Example |
|--------|---------|---------|
| config | `{name}.config.ts` | `audit.config.ts` |
| utils | `{name}.util.ts` | `format.util.ts` |
| hooks | `{domain}.hooks.ts` | `api.hooks.ts` |
| tables | `{domain}.table.tsx` | `userList.table.tsx` |
| contexts | `{Name}Context.tsx` | `AuthContext.tsx` |
| services | `{domain}.service.ts` | `scan.service.ts` |
| types | `{domain}.ts` (in `src/@types/`) | `user.ts` |
| redux slices | `{domain}.ts` (in `src/redux/slices/`) | `cart.ts` |
| auth | `auth.{purpose}.ts` | `auth.middleware.ts` |
| components | `{ComponentName}.tsx` | `DataTable.tsx` |
| co-located constants | `{kebab-name}.constants.ts` | `data-table.constants.ts` |
| co-located callbacks | `{kebab-name}.callbacks.ts` | `page.callbacks.ts` |
| co-located schemas | `{kebab-name}.schema.ts` | `login.schema.ts` |
| co-located types | `{kebab-name}.types.ts` | `data-table.types.ts` |

Component files use PascalCase (`DataTable.tsx`), co-located files use kebab-case (`data-table.constants.ts`).
